@node "legal" "Legal mush"

This driver is SHAREWARE.  This version works around 3 minutes - at refresh rate 1 
(thats must be enough for testing), after stopps to work (You can exit from shape 
with the following keys:  LAlt+LShift+Control+ESC), and the demo-archive contains only 
the 256 color version.  (i think you discovered it..)

Use it at your own risk.
If you want include this driver on a CD-ROM/or magazine i would be very happy when you
send me a free copy from it.

